reetmap.org/node/282412907\n| title       = Node: Shimabara-Kou (282412907)\n| website     = [[OpenStreetMap]]\n| date        = 2019-10-05\n| access-date = 2020-04-08\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"ekitan\">{{cite web\n| url         = https://ekitan.com/station/EnsenList?SFCODE=7683\n| title       = \u5cf6\u539f\u8239\u6d25\u99c5  {{pipe}} \u99c5\u63a2\n| trans-title = Shimabarafunatu Station {{pipe}} Station Search\n| language    = Japanese\n| website     = {{nihongo|\u99c5\u63a2|Ekitan}}\n| accessdate  = 2020-04-08\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"railway-gazette\">{{cite web\n| title     = Shimabara Railway {{pipe}} Organisations\n| url       = https://www.railwaygazette.com/knowledge-hub/shimabara-railway/53279.article\n| publisher = [[Railway Gazette International]]\n| access-date = 2020-04-08\n}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"nishinippon\">{{cite news\n| title       = \u5cf6\u539f\u9244\u9053\u304c\uff11\uff11\uff11\u5e74\u8a18\u5ff5\u8a8c \uff33\uff2c\u3001\u30c7\u30a3\u30fc\u30bc\u30eb\u8eca\u4e21\u6e80\u8f09 \u5ec3\u6b62\u306e\u6cbf\u7dda\u98a8\u666f\u3082\n| trans-title = Shimabara Railway's 111 year commemorative magazine, with diesel locomotives and scenery around closed stations\n| language    = Japanese\n| website     = [[Nishinippon Shimbun]]\n| url         = https://www.nishinippon.co.jp/item/n/510106/\n| date        = 2019-05-15\n| access-date = 2020-04-08\n}}</ref>\n}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Commons category-inline}}\n* {{Official site|https://www.shimatetsu.co.jp/railway/}} {{in lang|ja}}\n* [https://www.navitime.co.jp/diagram/timetable?lineId=00000781&node=00006619 Navitime station timetable] {{in lang|ja}}\n* [https://transit.yahoo.co.jp/station/top/28499/ Yahoo! Transit Japan] {{in lang|ja}}\n\n{{Shimabara Railway Line}}\n\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 1913]]\n[[Category:Railway stations in Nagasaki Prefecture]]\n[[Category:1913 establishments in Japan]]\n[[Category:Stations of Shimabara Railway]]\n", "name_user": "RubenSchade", "label": "safe", "comment": "